Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.44,0:12:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}なんという負け惜しみ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:16.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}たっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.44,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うっ！
