Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.07,0:12:27.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}あああ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}ああ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.21,0:12:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うぐ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.62,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\c&Hffffff&}うっ！
